author: Sagarika Jaisinghani
title: EMERGING MARKETS-Russian rouble leads currencies higher as oil rebounds - Reuters
description: The Russian rouble led gains among emerging market currencies on Tuesday as oil rebounded from its worst week this year, while a jump in Hong Kong-listed technology stocks lifted the regional equities index.
content:
